text.tspan: More than just a build server!
Jenkins is the leading open-source continuous integration server, used the world over for
building everything from Java to C, to Ruby, Python and Erlang and many more projects.
But Jenkins can do so much more! Automating sysadmin tasks and integrating with other
tools like RunDeck, Gerrit, GitHub and more.
- Over 400 plugins to enable almost any workflow
- Crontab-like scheduling, but with monitoring and queueing
- Manual triggering of tasks or cascading execution
- Parameterized jobs enable passing custom data when running tasks
Then navigate to http://localhost:8080 and configure everything from your browser!
- Build plugins in Java or Ruby
- Command line tool and SSH API for easy scripting
